# Free Hosting Deployment Plan — ChatDB (Approved)

## Strategy
- **Backend** → **Render.com** free tier (Docker, Python/FastAPI)
- **Frontend** → **Vercel** free tier (React/Vite, global CDN)
- **Anti-sleep** → **UptimeRobot** pings `/api/health` every 5 min → no cold starts
- **Cost** → $0/month

## Execution Steps
1. Prepare deployment files (gitignore, render.yaml, vercel.json, Dockerfile updates)
2. Initialize Git repo & push to GitHub
3. Guide user through Render deployment
4. Guide user through Vercel deployment
5. Set up UptimeRobot to keep backend alive
6. Verify end-to-end
